comments.body:
The PR is ready, checks are green.

@Honny1, please have a look at the first 2 commits of this PR, where I made some updates to `IsPathAvailableOnMachine` so I could reuse it to determine whether the file containing the certificates is already mounted on the machine.

@jakecorrenti, please have a look at the third commit, where I have refactored `LocalhostSSHCopy` to run SCP and copy the file from the host to the machine.
